  <brief_title>Efficacy of Topical Capsaicin on Chronic Neck Pain</brief_title>
  <official_title>Efficacy of Topical Capsaicin on Chronic Neck Pain ; Double-blinded Randomized Trial</official_title>
  <sponsors>
